teqqen ɣer wansayen d tegnatin n usnulfu am tmedyazt i d ttawint tlawin deg lfuruh
ma iḥubb ik uḥeddad ak iselqem s tirgin ubeṛwaq
stut nni i d yeɛreḍ ugelliḍ ɣer tmeɣra teɣra timsal n tudert
fṛansa ṭelyan spanya swis biljik d timura i d yerzan di turuft
ma nger tamuɣli ar yisem n wungal a tagrest d wurɣu ad naf deg s sin yismawen mgaraden tegrest d tasemhayt
akken ad nessaweḍ ɣer yiswi nneɣ nebḍa anadi ɣef tlata yeḥricen
aɣyul n baba u jeddi rniɣ rrekba ɣer deffier
akiluṭamḍan d alef u rebɛa u miyya n yiṭamḍanen
